As you turn the coin over and over, you see the exquisite curves and strokes of a foreign language written in a circle around the center.\
"In rememberance of Kai, Dragon Lord of Time"\
You rack your brain, searching for the memories squirreled away... Then it hits you.

<em>"...And it's name was Kai, the benevolent one of Time. With it's mighty roar, it could send the world into a future time."</em>
